title: Update openai requirement from ^4.57.0 to ^4.77.0 in /src
body:
Updates the requirements on [openai](https://github.com/openai/openai-node) to permit the latest version.
Release notes

Sourced from openai's releases.

v4.77.0

4.77.0 (2024-12-17)

Full Changelog: v4.76.3...v4.77.0

Features

  • api: new o1 and GPT-4o models + preference fine-tuning (#1229) (2e872d4)

Chores

  • internal: fix some typos (#1227) (d51fcfe)
  • internal: spec update (#1230) (ed2b61d)
